⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Melina
node ER · ER · ⟦Melina:ER:ccd8e8⟧

WHO   — Melina — the kindling maiden with the burned eye
WHAT  — A mysterious, bodiless maiden born within the Erdtree, one eye sealed, who joins the Tarnished at the journey's start.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the journey to the Erdtree — companion of the Tarnished  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Her purpose, long burned into her, is to give herself as kindling and ignite the Flame of Ruin — the price of opening the way.
HOW   — She offers an accord — turning runes to strength and lending her horse-summoning ring — in exchange for passage to the foot of the Erdtree.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Gentle, resolute, and built to burn — she asks only to be carried to the fire.

